        <h1>The Crowbar Project</h1>
        <p>The Crowbar Project is an effort to build a complete, easy to use operational
          platform for everyone. It allows for groups of physical nodes to be
          transformed from bare-metal into production services within hours. Specific applications
          include (but are not limited to) Hadoop and OpenStack.</p>
